
Based on <https://cell2location.readthedocs.io/en/latest/notebooks/cell2location_tutorial.html#Cell2location:-spatial-mapping>

Needed to activate the Miniforge installation.

```bash
miniforge_activate_base
```

Instructions from cell2location README.

```bash
export PYTHONNOUSERSITE="literallyanyletters"
mamba create -y -n cell2loc_env python=3.9

conda activate cell2loc_env
pip install cell2location[tutorials]
```

Need to run code in a Jupyter notebook:

```bash
pip install ipykernel
```
